title: Nelson's Gravière Wave of the winter?
description:
Incredible Surfing winter 2013-2014 in Europe, some huge swell have been licking the Atlantic coast and some incredible waves have been ridden. Here is the wave Nelson Cloarec took early December 13 on the infamous spot of La Gravière, Hossegor, France. Some Rumors say it is the best wave ridden on at La Gravière in the last 4 years...
Footage Pietro Franca
Surfer Nelson Cloarec
